<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Four <rs type="material">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType"> frieze blocks</rs>, one in two fragments. a: a corner block; to the left, the last letters of <xref type="iAph">564</xref>. The block then juts forward, and<xref type="iAph"> 565</xref> begins on the front, protruding face (<measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.89</measure>). b: one block in two fragments. c: complete; d: two fragments. The lower edge is damaged, but the text can be restored from <xref type="iAph">569</xref>.</p>
</div>
